Title: Untitled Love
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/untitled-love
SetInCountry: Netherlands
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Rishabh Chauhan
AuthorCountry: India
Text: 'Kirdaar:


  Zindagi khudke lie jeena hi ek zariya hain aagey badne kaa naa jaane kis talaash
  main hain hum sab.


  Jo zindagi hum jee rahe hain abhi naa jaane kyu aisa lagta hain ki wahi shaksiyat
  hain bhi hum yaa nahi.


  Bachpan ka jo sapna tha asliyat nahi bana wajah bahut thi usein naa jee paane ki
  kuch logo ki mazburiyan thi aur kuch logo ka darr, naa jaane kyu apne aapko roka
  tha ki kubul kiya aisa kirdaar jo tumhaara tha hi nahi.


  Bachpan ka sapna jo tha hamara asli kirdaar himmat karte jeene ki toh jeene ka falsafaa
  kuch is tarah nikharta ki hamein khudki talaash nahi karni padti.


  Zindagi ki daud main bhul gaye hain ki kya kirdaar hain hamaara yaha, naa jaane
  kiski zindagi ka bojh lie jee rahe hain.


  Magar dil main jo baat thi ek kasak thi usko bol paane kaa jazba kisi tarah mil
  jaata toh mera kirdaar bhi yaad rakha jaata.


  Abb aise raaston pe chalte jaa rahe hain kisi aur ka kirdaar apna samajhke jeete
  jaa rahe hain, itni uljhan bhari hain zindagi ki khudko apne apse dur karte jaa
  rahe hain.


  Mehroom hua kuch logo se jo apna kirdaar bakhubi nibha rahe thein, zindagi ki daud
  main aagey bhi jaa rahe thein khush rakhna apne parivaar ko unka tha pehla farz
  par uss farz ko nibhate hue woh khudko bhulte jaa rahein thein, kya woh kirdaar
  nibhana jaayaz tha zindagi main apne wajood ko chupake rakhna jaayaz tha naa jaane
  ye baat kisi ko samjha paana mumkin hain yaa nahi magar jeene ka andaaz dekha yahi
  har kahi.


  Shadbo ke sahaare ye kehna chahta hu apni baat yahi rakhna chahta hu ki jeeye jo
  bhi kirdaar kuch iss tarah jeeye ki subah ki kiran ka intezaar usein jeene ke lie
  raat ko usko bhulne ke lie nahi..'
